    <entry>
      <title>hello-hexo</title>
      <link href="/2026/05/04/hello-hexo/"/>
      <url>/2026/05/04/hello-hexo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h1 id="安装Hexo并初始化博客"><a href="#安装Hexo并初始化博客" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo并初始化博客"></a>安装Hexo并初始化博客</h1><h2 id="全局安装Hexo-cli"><a href="#全局安装Hexo-cli" class="headerlink" title="全局安装Hexo cli"></a>全局安装Hexo cli</h2><p>终端执行以下命令，全局安装Hexo命令行工具</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hexo  -v</code>验证安装成功</p><h2 id="执行初始化命令，生成Hexo博客基础结构"><a href="#执行初始化命令，生成Hexo博客基础结构" class="headerlink" title="执行初始化命令，生成Hexo博客基础结构"></a>执行初始化命令，生成Hexo博客基础结构</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir blog（自定义路径）</span><br><span class="line">cd blog</span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装博客依赖包</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="查看Hexo博客目录结构"><a href="#查看Hexo博客目录结构" class="headerlink" title="查看Hexo博客目录结构"></a>查看Hexo博客目录结构</h2><p>初始化完成后，blog路径下会生成以下核心文件&#x2F;核心文件夹:</p><ul><li>_config.yml: Hexo全局配置文件，用于配置博客<strong>标题、主题、部署信息</strong></li><li>node_modules：用于存储已安装的各类依赖包，package.json用于查看Hexo的本本以及相关依赖包的版本</li><li>source&#x2F;：存放博客原始内容，_posts&#x2F;路径用于存放所有博客文章(Markdown格式)</li><li>themes&#x2F;：存放博客主题，默认主题为landscape</li><li>public&#x2F;: Hexo 生成的静态网页文件</li><li>scaffolds&#x2F;: 文章模板文件，新建文章时会基于模板生成</li></ul><h1 id="本地预览Hexo博客"><a href="#本地预览Hexo博客" class="headerlink" title="本地预览Hexo博客"></a>本地预览Hexo博客</h1><ol><li><p>生成静态网页文件</p> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate # 简写: hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p></li><li><p>启动本地服务器</p> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server # 简写： hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p></li><li><p>预览博客<br>  打开浏览器，访问<a href="http://localhost:4000，即可看到博客页面">http://localhost:4000，即可看到博客页面</a></p></li></ol><h1 id="部署Hexo博客到Githb-Pages"><a href="#部署Hexo博客到Githb-Pages" class="headerlink" title="部署Hexo博客到Githb Pages"></a>部署Hexo博客到Githb Pages</h1><p>将Hexo博客部署到Github Pages，实现公网访问</p><ol><li><p>准备Github仓库<br>登录Github，新建一个仓库，仓库名必须为<strong>Github用户名.github.io</strong> (如：zhuanghb28.github.io)</p></li><li><p><strong>配置部署信息</strong>，在<code>_config.yml</code>文件中添加以下内容</p> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: git@github.com:zhuanghb28/zhuanghb28.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装Hexo部署插件<br>安装hexo-deployer-git插件（用于将静态文件部署到Github）</p> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>部署博客到Github<br>将Hexo生成的静态文件推送到Github仓库</p> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo deploy # 简写: hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p></li></ol><p>在执行<code>hexo d</code>部署成功后，新增了.deploy_git，public，.gitignore，三者的关系如下：</p><ul><li>source: 用于存放图片，.md文档，各类页面</li><li>public：将source文件夹里的Markdown文档，转成index.html，再结合主题进行渲染；执行hexo g生成</li><li>.deploy_git:将public文件夹的内容提交到Github生成，内容与public文件夹基本一致；执行hexo d生成</li></ul><h1 id="主题安装和设置"><a href="#主题安装和设置" class="headerlink" title="主题安装和设置"></a>主题安装和设置</h1><h2 id="选择并安装主题"><a href="#选择并安装主题" class="headerlink" title="选择并安装主题"></a>选择并安装主题</h2><p>可以在<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">Hexo主题库</a>中选择主题，以bufferfly为例，安装步骤如下：</p><ol><li>下载bufferfly主题并放入博客的<code>themes</code>路径下</li><li>修改根目录的<code>_config.yml</code>文件，将<code>theme</code>参数设置为<code>bufferfly</code>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="bufferfly导航栏设置"><a href="#bufferfly导航栏设置" class="headerlink" title="bufferfly导航栏设置"></a>bufferfly导航栏设置</h2><p>修改<code>themes/bufferfly/_config.yml</code>配置文件，</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">  # </span><span class="language-bash">Home: / || fas fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">  # </span><span class="language-bash">List||fas fa-list:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">  # </span><span class="language-bash">  Music: /music/ || fas fa-music</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">  # </span><span class="language-bash">  Movie: /movies/ || fas fa-video</span></span><br><span class="line">  首页: / || fas fa-home</span><br><span class="line">  归档: /archives/ || fas fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">  标签: /tags/ || fas fa-tags</span><br><span class="line">  目录: /categories/ || fas fa-folder-open</span><br><span class="line">  友情链接: /link/ || fas fa-link</span><br><span class="line">  关于我们: /about/ || fas fa-heart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2026/05/04/hello-hexo/image.png" alt="alt text" title="导航图"><br>若要生成&#x2F;categories，执行命令生成对应的page</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>则可在&#x2F;source路径下生成categories的路径，路径下有index.md文件，新增type行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type: categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可在<code>localhost:4000/categories</code>页面自动汇总博客文章Front-matter中<strong>categories</strong>字段的目录。</p><h2 id="hexo博客搜索功能"><a href="#hexo博客搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="hexo博客搜索功能"></a>hexo博客搜索功能</h2><p>添加搜索功能，安装hexo-generato-search插件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>并修改配置文件<code>themes/bufferfly/_config.yml</code>中如下片段，在search字段中的use填写为”local_search”</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Choose: algolia_search / local_search / docsearch</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># leave it empty if you don&#x27;t need search</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">use:</span> <span class="string">local_search</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="hexo新建、编辑文章"><a href="#hexo新建、编辑文章" class="headerlink" title="hexo新建、编辑文章"></a>hexo新建、编辑文章</h1><h2 id="新建文章"><a href="#新建文章" class="headerlink" title="新建文章"></a>新建文章</h2><p>创建文章前要先选定模板，在hexo中也叫做布局。hexo支持三种布局(layout)：post(默认)、draft(草稿)、page。<br>在博客目录下输入命令，会使用默认post布局，自动在<code>source/post_</code>目录生成text1.md文件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new text1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开text1.md可看到Front-matter内容，用于设置该文章的一些变量，比如title、author、tags、categories等等，可在scaffolds&#x2F;目录下自定义三种布局。</p><h2 id="为Hexo新建文章指定存放目录"><a href="#为Hexo新建文章指定存放目录" class="headerlink" title="为Hexo新建文章指定存放目录"></a>为Hexo新建文章指定存放目录</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new post -p c++/hello-c++  # 注意生成的md文件的title为post，可手动修改title</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">注意生成的md文件的title为hello-python</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new post hello-python -p python/hello-python </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成的预览画面如下图：<br><img src="/2026/05/04/hello-hexo/image2.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h2 id="新建草稿"><a href="#新建草稿" class="headerlink" title="新建草稿"></a>新建草稿</h2><p>使用以下命令可在<code>source\</code>目录下创建<code>_drafts</code>目录，并生成draft1.md文件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new draft draft1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当编辑完草稿，可以把文章推送到<code>_posts</code>目录</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo publish &lt;file_name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以使用<code>hexo g --draft &amp;&amp; hexo s --draft</code>预览已有的草稿。</p><h2 id="插入图片"><a href="#插入图片" class="headerlink" title="插入图片"></a>插入图片</h2><p>插入图片的Markdown语法</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt</span>](<span class="link">path</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中，</p><ul><li>path表示图片的路径，可使用绝对或者相对路径</li><li>alt是可选的，表示图片无法加载时的替代描述文本</li></ul><p>在hexo中，还需要为图片制定一个资源文件夹，有两种方式插入图片</p><ol><li>将所有文章的图片放到source&#x2F;images文件夹，然后使用markdown语句引用图片，适合少量图片的项目，图片一多就比较混乱</li><li>安装npm插件 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>为每一篇文章单独创建一个资源文件夹，将图片保存其中，具体步骤如下：</li></ol><ul><li>在博客根目录打开_config.yml文件做如下修改：  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yaml post_asset_folder: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>使用<code>hexo new text2</code>命令创建text2文章，即可看到<code>source/_post</code>路径下创建了同名的文件夹，编辑.md文件时，可使用相对路径进行引用</li></ul><ol start="4"><li>清除缓存，发布 <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="为私密文章加密"><a href="#为私密文章加密" class="headerlink" title="为私密文章加密"></a>为私密文章加密</h2><p>首先，需要安装hexo-encrypt插件，</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-blog-encrypt --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完成后，配置根目录下的_config.yml，添加以下配置项</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Hexo Encrypt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">encrypt:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 启用加密功能</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">abstract:</span> <span class="string">这里有一些加密的内容，需要密码才能继续阅读。</span> <span class="comment"># 加密文章的摘要提示</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">message:</span> <span class="string">嘿，这里需要密码才能访问。</span> <span class="comment"># 密码输入框上方的提示信息</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">private</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">password:</span> <span class="string">your_tag_password</span> <span class="comment"># 该标签的密码</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wrong_pass_message:</span> <span class="string">哦，这是一个无效的密码，请检查并重试。</span> <span class="comment"># 密码错误提示</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wrong_hash_message:</span> <span class="string">哦，这些解密内容无法验证，但你仍然可以查看。</span> <span class="comment"># 哈希校验失败提示</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># silent: true # 如果设置为 true，将禁用加密相关的日志输出</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编写加密文章有两种方式：1. 为单篇文章设置密码； 2. 配置跟路径下的_config.yml中的配置来对多篇文章设置默认密码或基于标签的密码</p><ul><li><p><strong>方式一</strong>：单篇文章设置密码<br>  在Hexo文章的Markdown文件中(例如<code>source/_posts/your-post.md</code>)的Front-matter添加<code>password</code>字段，并设置密码</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">hello-hexo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">password:</span> <span class="string">your_password</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>方式二</strong>：为tags中的某个标签批量（如private）设置密码，则任何带有该标签的文章均会被加密，只需在文章的Front-matter添加对应的标签即可。</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">hello-hexo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span> [<span class="string">hexo</span>, <span class="string">private</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> blog </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> hexo </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
